title: Dalida - Arabian Songs

Dalida - Arabian Songs

Dalida, born Iolanda Cristina Gigliotti, was a world-famous singer and actress born in Egypt with Italian origins but naturalised French. She received 55 gold records and was the first singer to receive a diamond disc.
